62
00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:31.110
There is a quick overview of the changes made to the WordPress core.

63
00:04:31.140 --> 00:04:35.340
This is a really great way to check out what functions have been added.

64
00:04:37.650 --> 00:04:41.970
On the right, there's a list of APIs available in WordPress.

65
00:04:44.040 --> 00:04:47.980
We'll be exploring most of these functions throughout the course.

66
00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:50.770
Let's take a look at how to search for code.

67
00:04:50.790 --> 00:04:53.350
You don't need to follow along for this part.

68
00:04:53.370 --> 00:04:56.570
You can sit back and relax in the search form.

69
00:04:56.580 --> 00:05:00.480
Let's try searching for the blog info function.

70
00:05:02.720 --> 00:05:05.370
This is one of the functions we've learned about.

71
00:05:05.390 --> 00:05:08.250
The reference will return a few results.

72
00:05:08.270 --> 00:05:10.460
Let's check out the first results.

73
00:05:12.630 --> 00:05:16.750
WordPress does an incredible job of documenting its functions.

74
00:05:16.770 --> 00:05:23.040
If we're interested in learning about a specific piece of code, we'll be able to search for it through

75
00:05:23.040 --> 00:05:24.420
the code reference.

76
00:05:24.450 --> 00:05:28.380
This page will document everything you'd like to know about the function.

77
00:05:28.380 --> 00:05:30.390
Let's run through it together.

78
00:05:30.420 --> 00:05:35.810
We've already reviewed the description parameters and more information sections.

79
00:05:35.820 --> 00:05:38.600
These sections are self explanatory.

80
00:05:38.610 --> 00:05:41.910
The next section of this page is called Source.

81
00:05:44.010 --> 00:05:48.430
The Source section documents the original function definition.

82
00:05:48.450 --> 00:05:52.390
WordPress is completely transparent with its code base.

83
00:05:52.410 --> 00:05:57.060
You can study WordPress functions for a better understanding of its behavior.

84
00:05:57.090 --> 00:06:01.100
WordPress will even give you the file name down further.

85
00:06:01.110 --> 00:06:03.630
There's another section called related.

86
00:06:03.660 --> 00:06:09.170
